# Day 824

![[https://x.com/ConorChepenik/status/1804942236200706441](https://x.com/ConorChepenik/status/1804942236200706441)](https://miro.medium.com/1*jgY09SKliv-RKcg7ktC3bQ.png)

What's the point of the above? That we can get better by ourselves, but doing it with other humans is way more fun, enjoyable, and rewarding. So when you get the chance work with other people do it.

![](https://miro.medium.com/0*smRw6KTkhbt3f_xE)

On another note I've been going down a [Billy Carson rabbit hole](https://www.youtube.com/@ForbiddenKnowledge1) and the wisdom from ancient civilizations is fascinating. Excited to keep learning about our ancestors.

6/23/24

Conor Jay Chepenik
